#. type: Title ###
#, no-wrap
msgid "Clipboard encryption and decryption is broken in *Kleopatra* ([[!tails_ticket 19329]])"
msgstr ""
"L'encriptatge i el desencriptatge del porta-retalls estan trencats a "
"*Kleopatra* ([[!tails_ticket 19329]])"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "To fix this:"
msgstr "Per solucionar això:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Choose **Applications**&nbsp;▸ **Utilities**&nbsp;▸ **Terminal** to open a "
"terminal."
msgstr ""
"Trieu **Aplicacions**&nbsp;▸ **Utilitats**&nbsp;▸ **Terminal** per obrir un "
"terminal."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Execute the following command in the terminal:"
msgstr "Executeu l'ordre següent al terminal:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "       unset QT_QPA_PLATFORM & kleopatra &\n"
msgstr "       unset QT_QPA_PLATFORM & kleopatra &\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   This only works if *Kleopatra* has never been started since Tails started.\n"
"   Otherwise, execute this command and try again:\n"
msgstr ""
"   Això només funciona si *Kleopatra* no s'ha iniciat des que s'ha iniciat "
"Tails.\n"
"   En cas contrari, executeu aquesta ordre i torneu-ho a provar:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "       killall kleopatra\n"
msgstr "       killall kleopatra\n"

#. type: Title ###
#, no-wrap
msgid "AppImages like *Feather* wallet and *Bitcoin-Qt* fail to load ([[!tails_ticket 19326]])"
msgstr ""
"Imatges d'aplicacions com la cartera *Feather* i *Bitcoin-Qt* no es poden "
"carregar ([[!tails_ticket 19326]])"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
